{"about_the_game":"<strong>THIS GAME IS DESIGNED TO BE ENJOYED FOR ABOUT 20 MINUTES</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">---------------------------------</h2><br>Chase Fox's fifth game.<br><br>Floralgraphic Memory is a tiny fantasy pastel drama kinetic visual novel that tells a story of a teenager named Rose who whisked himself away to another world after decided to skip school today.<br><br>This game is a kinetic visual novel, which means it will not provide choices that shape your story or any other interactions. The only ways to interact with the game are to click to move the story forward, click to explore things in the some scenes and use the scene jumper to jump to specific scenes in the story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2>Rose is a teenager who decides to skip school today for an unknown reason. He then whisked himself away to another world full of whimsies and magic.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Genre</h2>Short, Light, Fantasy, Pastel Drama<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Original Art, Music &amp; Sound Design</strong><br></li><li><strong>Scene Jumper</strong> : press Esc at any time to bring up a pause menu that will let you jump to specific scenes in the story, no save slot required<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570830/extras/steampage_scene_jumper.png?t=1714620577\" /><br></li><li><strong>Hand-Crafted Art </strong><br>This game features digital art and watercolor art.<br>Right-click at any point in the game to see the making process of the art.<br><br>Digital Art<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570830/extras/steampage_handcrafted_art1.png?t=1714620577\" /><br>Watercolor Art<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570830/extras/steampage_handcrafted_art2.png?t=1714620577\" /><br></li><li><strong>Inspectable Environment</strong><br>In some 